"<phrase>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>Address Book</quote> context "
"menu.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Bildschirmfoto des Kontextmenüs <quote>Adressbuch hinzufügen</quote> "
"von &kaddressbook;.</phrase>"

